# Catch-all routing rule consulted by `transport_maps`.
#
# Every recipient at inbox.boliganalyse.ai is dispatched to the
# `inbound-pipe` transport defined in master.cf. The full envelope
# recipient (including the original local part) is preserved and made
# available to the pipe script via Postfix's argument expansion.
/^.*@inbox\.boliganalyse\.ai$/  inbound-pipe:
